nodes.name: 3-Oxopropanoate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (decarboxylating, CoA-acetylating)

nodes.name: acetyl-CoA:carbon-dioxide ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Acetyl-CoA + HCO3- <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + Malonyl-CoA

nodes.name: (S)-Methylmalonate semialdehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase (CoA-propanoylating)
nodes.rxn: (S)-Methylmalonate semialdehyde + CoA + NAD+ <=> Propanoyl-CoA + CO2 + NADH + H+

nodes.name: propanoate:CoA ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Propanoate + CoA <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + Propanoyl-CoA

nodes.name: 2-oxobutanoate:ferredoxin 2-oxidoreductase (CoA-propanoylating)
nodes.rxn: 2 Oxidized ferredoxin + 2-Oxobutanoate + CoA <=> 2 Reduced ferredoxin + Propanoyl-CoA + CO2 + 2 H+

nodes.name: propanoyl-CoA:electron-transfer flavoprotein 2,3-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Electron-transferring flavoprotein + Propanoyl-CoA <=> Reduced electron-transferring flavoprotein + Propenoyl-CoA

nodes.name: Succinate:CoA ligase (ADP-forming)

nodes.name: Succinate:CoA ligase (GDP-forming)

nodes.name: propanal:NAD+ oxidoreductase (CoA-propanoylating)
nodes.rxn: Propanal + NAD+ + CoA <=> Propanoyl-CoA + NADH + H+

nodes.name: enzyme N6-(dihydrolipoyl)lysine:NAD+ oxidoreductase

nodes.name: 2-(alpha-Hydroxypropyl)thiamine diphosphate + Enzyme N6-(lipoyl)lysine <=> Enzyme N6-(S-propyldihydrolipoyl)lysine + Thiamin diphosphate
nodes.rxn: 2-(alpha-Hydroxypropyl)thiamine diphosphate + Enzyme N6-(lipoyl)lysine <=> Enzyme N6-(S-propyldihydrolipoyl)lysine + Thiamin diphosphate

nodes.name: propanoyl-CoA:enzyme N6-(dihydrolipoyl)lysine S-propanoyltransferase
